{"tid":1463730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到底而家係癱瘓機場定和你飛","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:40:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:01:39.000Z","uid":63822,"like":14,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"86defcb741db301a2f72468f1faf94cfab332528","tid":1463730,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:40:36.000Z","msg":"又話講撚到突破盲點，知道機場係春袋<br />\n<br />\n又話咩打經濟牌，要政府日日蝕大錢<br />\n<br />\n而家block人啦，想停機啦，先黎講咩會影響人會輸輿論<br />\n<br />\n而家唔係表達訴求呀，係打擊經濟呀<br />\n<br />\n上個星期表撚左3日啦，仲唔夠呀？<br />\n<br />\n我唔認為爆眼一事既輿論壓力都cover唔到阻人登機<br />\n<br />\n又話咩機場係皇牌，係經濟命脈<br />\n<br />\n個個係下面打卡唱歌，叫人上去塞離景就又鬼又送頭<br />\n<br />\n上面塞都係和理非黎嫁，冇人叫係勇武衝呀<br />\n<br />\n下面接機大堂鳩座果班連和理非都唔係，稱呼你做和理非簡直係侮辱和理非<br />\n<br />\n你地根本係為打卡，圍爐，嘻嘻哈哈同溫層"},{"pid":"c809ac7eec7264a298ea67b9c4e2e5ffb12f188b","tid":1463730,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:42:39.000Z","msg":"不服來辦呀"},{"pid":"09a20afdab711f455c875a62e4981e4c024dbb68","tid":1463730,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:43:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56d448b355ef365c4d8c70eb5482207f2a031b4a","tid":1463730,"uid":68471,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:43:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},{"pid":"abd3ad1eddc91fb7d7f90c57641f7a0a79b8175c","tid":1463730,"uid":63822,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:44:19.000Z","msg":"而家係政府明知機場咁既情況都叫人照check in入<br />\n<br />\n我地一早講撚明要癱機場嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n政府叫人check in我地就放人？<br />\n<br />\n咁乜撚都唔洗做啦<br />\n<br />\n叫佢地要屌就屌政府！"},{"pid":"4ded6f4411f3019cfc07fa9febe9322206d51419","tid":1463730,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56d448b355ef365c4d8c70eb5482207f2a031b4a","tid":1463730,"uid":68471,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:43:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:45:44.000Z","msg":"問題係現場放得一個過就要放埋第二個<br />\n<br />\n放下放下有班人直情推gip衝<br />\n<br />\n話撚明癱瘓<br />\n<br />\n現場共識係一個都唔撚放"},{"pid":"156d3c96d561bdf432a4fc114b0ac74817733996","tid":1463730,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:47:07.000Z","msg":"負皮果d出黎講兩句呀<br />\n<br />\n係arrival坐一日令政府損失幾多錢呀？"},{"pid":"c1cd2fb9c64fa5e032edab70aa9b4704356b0ca9","tid":1463730,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:48:41.000Z","msg":"我睇唔撚到樓下班人同2014金鐘旺角果兩條村有咩分別喎"},{"pid":"3e34d04dec1dc609bc268c4ad96b074ff5ad44b3","tid":1463730,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:51:35.000Z","msg":"有冇高手諗到點樣唔得罪任何人又可以令航班停飛，令政府蝕錢既方法呀？<br />\n<br />\n出黎等我開下眼界？"},{"pid":"8c7654a204b09b64bf9e57cf48d95e88018f4b64","tid":1463730,"uid":20696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:52:29.000Z","msg":"我覺得今日人唔夠多<br />\n要日日搞癱瘓一定無可能<br />\n尋日多人因為民憤高<br />\n有啲甚至罷工入黎<br />\n但好多人尋日入完當贖罪券今日就唔再入<br />\n唔夠人格硬癱都冇用，癱唔到，啲人照樣入到<br />\n<br />\n我覺得一星期定一/兩日多人到好似尋日咁<br />\nJam死交通塞爆機場等機管局自己停<br />\n唔好連續兩日搞，連續濟留兩日嘅旅行都好慘"},{"pid":"973771fc44f7aa19cb78099120b8eefc0742de56","tid":1463730,"uid":244607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:52:29.000Z","msg":"不分化"},{"pid":"32a88ae63dd122079331078a3b65599402f30c68","tid":1463730,"uid":261330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:53:59.000Z","msg":"巴打，我同你一樣甘諗，而家好灰，個個係下面打卡唔知做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b2d463a2b2463b6920cf672d1f8a4f27b9e700","tid":1463730,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8c7654a204b09b64bf9e57cf48d95e88018f4b64","tid":1463730,"uid":20696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:52:29.000Z","msg":"我覺得今日人唔夠多<br />\n要日日搞癱瘓一定無可能<br />\n尋日多人因為民憤高<br />\n有啲甚至罷工入黎<br />\n但好多人尋日入完當贖罪券今日就唔再入<br />\n唔夠人格硬癱都冇用，癱唔到，啲人照樣入到<br />\n<br />\n我覺得一星期定一/兩日多人到好似尋日咁<br />\nJam死交通塞爆機場等機管局自己停<br />\n唔好連續兩日搞，連續濟留兩日嘅旅行都好慘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:55:08.000Z","msg":"呢樣野頭先現場都討論過<br />\n<br />\n就係要佢地無限期滯留，搵駐洗領事，自然會向政府施壓，政府又清唔撚到場<br />\n<br />\n留個炸彈比政府拆，唔係我地拆<br />\n<br />\n個個都好撚慘就比佢上機，咁香港人唔撚慘咩"},{"pid":"6fb0028bb99bb04168a931ef27fb9497ef61ef75","tid":1463730,"uid":111934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:55:09.000Z","msg":"香港人唔團結啫<br />\n如果罷工罷得成使乜搞機場, 使乜勇武呀<br />\n個個都鬼咁鍾意返工, 工又罷唔成<br />\n明明集體罷工係最簡單又唔使流血<br />\n結果逼到退而求其次要搞機場<br />\n變咗和理非又唔係勇武又唔係<br />\n兩面不是人"},{"pid":"8b0b17a83fc6f7f146fd54332ca352728ba75867","tid":1463730,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32a88ae63dd122079331078a3b65599402f30c68","tid":1463730,"uid":261330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:53:59.000Z","msg":"巴打，我同你一樣甘諗，而家好灰，個個係下面打卡唔知做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:55:45.000Z","msg":"係呀，我同幾個手足落去叫到聲都沙哂仲要比人屈鬼"},{"pid":"8706384c0bb98c5a451adc3c8e4db9e5d3e22ddf","tid":1463730,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fb0028bb99bb04168a931ef27fb9497ef61ef75","tid":1463730,"uid":111934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:55:09.000Z","msg":"香港人唔團結啫<br />\n如果罷工罷得成使乜搞機場, 使乜勇武呀<br />\n個個都鬼咁鍾意返工, 工又罷唔成<br />\n明明集體罷工係最簡單又唔使流血<br />\n結果逼到退而求其次要搞機場<br />\n變咗和理非又唔係勇武又唔係<br />\n兩面不是人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:57:57.000Z","msg":"我唔明，都入撚左黎啦，你係下面做乜柒<br />\n<br />\n如果所有航班正常運作都冇所謂，咁洗撚入黎咩<br />\n<br />\n要同旅客宣傳去酒店同旅遊區好撚過啦"},{"pid":"666721bd3f092e00cf7cfd802453d2ec606f905e","tid":1463730,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:01:58.000Z","msg":"下面坐得好撚開心呀？<br />\n<br />\n上面比人圍屌，屌到穿到仲堅持緊呀<br />\n<br />\n叫人還眼？叫下就得嫁啦？<br />\n<br />\n係就唔洗抗爭啦，去睇流星許願好撚過啦"},{"pid":"ebc0255b7c2c5f55b12c17a8a14cac0d7d8e32ab","tid":1463730,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:04:19.000Z","msg":"坐樓下無撚用果班入黎講兩句啦"},{"pid":"2aceb445fe723f57bbfb3fc522704331242ce084","tid":1463730,"uid":6955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:05:02.000Z","msg":"塞佢老母"},{"pid":"43c6a6ea066cc8f60c4e9f975847074b1b6b6d47","tid":1463730,"uid":269287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:06:07.000Z","msg":"又黎互屌,無眼睇"},{"pid":"91fe622ead589c13e6a7edfc14e5a4a1de9c46da","tid":1463730,"uid":181283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:13:15.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"bf2225284f2192a3fd5a7b8820718da7398f19fc","tid":1463730,"uid":196578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:17:36.000Z","msg":"入唔入機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2032ef45209689ba2a33b0747e9e4d2a4d3940a1","tid":1463730,"uid":113525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:24:38.000Z","msg":"支持！"},{"pid":"d624fa87eb443b359df6e3a51e35c5140cbada36","tid":1463730,"uid":257728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:25:37.000Z","msg":"拋磚引玉<br />\n<br />\n[抗爭案例]北愛爾蘭炸左倫敦三十年!! 香港呢???<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463910\" da